{"query":"query filterStudies(
	$studyIds: [Int]!,
	$countries: [String],
	$states: [String],
	$cities: [String],
	$overallStatuses: [OverallStatusType],
	$interventionTypes: [InterventionType],
	$phases: [PhaseType],
	$studyTypes: [StudyType],
  $yearBeg: Int,
  $yearEnd: Int,
  $orderBy: String,
	$order: TypeEnumOrder,
  $limit: Int,
	$offset: Int,
) {
	studies {
		filter(
			studyIds: $studyIds,
			countries: $countries,
			states: $states,
			cities: $cities,
			overallStatuses: $overallStatuses,
			interventionTypes: $interventionTypes,
			phases: $phases,
			studyTypes: $studyTypes,
			yearBeg: $yearBeg,
			yearEnd: $yearEnd,
			orderBy: $orderBy,
			order: $order,
  		limit: $limit,
			offset: $offset,
		) {
			studyId,
			briefTitle,
			locations {
				locationId,
				status,
				facility {
					name,
					city,
					state,
					country
				}
			},
			overallStatus,
			interventions {
				interventionType,
				name
			},
			conditions {
				conditionId,
				condition,
			},
			phase,
			studyType,
			startDate
		}
	}
}","variables":{"studyIds":[704,24225,46262,47065],"yearBeg":2005,"yearEnd":2007},"operationName":"filterStudies"}

{"query":"query filterStudies(

	$offset: Int,
) {
	studies {

			interventionTypes: $interventionTypes,
			phases: $phases,
			studyTypes: $studyTypes,
			yearBeg: $yearBeg,
			yearEnd: $yearEnd,
			orderBy: $orderBy,
			order: $order,
  		limit: $limit,
			offset: $offset,
		) {
			studyId,

			locations {
				status,
				facility {
					name,
					city,
					state,
					country
				}
			},
			overallStatus,
      studyMeshTerms {
        meshTermType,

          term,
				},
			},

			startDate,
		}
	}
}","variables":{"studyIds":[704,24225,46262,47065],"yearBeg":2005,"yearEnd":2007},"operationName":"filterStudies"}
